Advices:
--------
        * edit configure-android to automatically check and use
          env. variable ANDROID_NDK_DIR (or something alike)
        * edit configure-android to get command line params:
               + ndk-dir
               + abi target
               + djvulibre sources directory
               + other different compile params (like fexceptions)
        * edit configure-android to be able to compile djvulibre
          from any directory (not only current)